      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（サニピのメンバーは早々に休ませた。前日だからと）\n（特別なことをやっても、緊張だけが高まってしまう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I send the members of Sunny Peace to bed early.)\n(Doing special rehearsals just because it’s the night before will only make them more nervous.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.523958383003871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}くん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 9.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（布団に寝転がった俺が見上げると）\n（そこには麻奈が浮かんでいた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I look up from the futon where I’m lying down‚)\n(and Mana appears above me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "スカートの中、見えそうだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can almost see up your skirt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 16.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "幽霊のパンツ見ても、しょうがないでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the use in seeing ghost panties?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "まあな……興味があるわけでもないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. And I’m not really interested in that anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 24
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうデリカシーのないこと言わない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! Be a little more tactful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 26.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ところで幽霊って、実際の所どうなんだ？\nトイレ行ったりとか風呂入ったりとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ what is it actually like for ghosts in that department?\nDo you take baths and go to the bathroom?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "出来る訳ないでしょ。実体がないんだから……\nそれよりいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I don’t. I don’t have a body.\nAnyway‚ are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.32178978317086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……何が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 40.4666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "つまんないこと言ってごまかそうとしてもダメ\nさくらちゃんのこと。気になってるんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t try to distract me by talking about trivial things.\nI’m talking about Sakura. You’re worried about her‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.39476200739543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 46.8333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈には全てお見通しか）\n（俺の頭にあるのは、さくらの心臓のことだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mana sees right through me.)\n(I’ve got Sakura’s heart on my mind right now.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらの悩みは分からない。だが琴乃と麻奈が）\n（関係しているような気がしてならない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I don’t know what’s troubling Sakura right now. But I can’t shake the feeling)\n(that it has something to do with Kotono and Mana.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（そうだとしたら……やはり心臓のことを麻奈に）\n（話すべきなのだろうか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(And if I’m right… then maybe I really should tell Mana)\n(about the heart transplant.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 65.0666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　{user}くん\n今聞こえてきてるのって……さくらちゃんの歌声……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}?\nIs that Sakura’s singing I’m hearing right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうだな\nでもどこから……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it is.\nBut where is it coming from?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.3333333333344,
          "startTime": 75.83333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 75.4666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 75.4666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 75.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん……\nごめんなさい、うるさかったですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}… The lesson is\nI’m sorry. Was I too loud?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "平気だよ。起きてたし\n……眠れないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. I was awake anyway.\nCan’t sleep?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 87.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ…………\n……違いますね。はい、眠れなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ uh…\nThat was a lie. Yeah‚ I can’t sleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 94.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "…………不思議ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s so strange‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "私、どうして、今ここにいるんだろうって\n考えてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I keep wondering what\nI’m even doing here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 102.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "…………今の状況は、想像してなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You never imagined yourself being in this situation?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "想像する訳ないですよ～\nだってアイドルなんて全然知らなかったんだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course not!\nI mean‚ I didn’t know anything about idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 112.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "それが、胸がドキンとなって、事務所に入って\nデビューして、なんだか分からないうちに注目されて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But then… my heart led me here; I joined this agency‚\nI made my idol debut‚ and somehow I’m in the spotlight now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……目まぐるしい速さだったもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It did happen at a dizzying speed‚ huh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 125.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "はい。でも、もしかしたら、こうなるって\n全部分かってたのかもしれないなぁ……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But I wonder if a part of me\nknew that all of this was going to happen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
