      "text": "いえ……ここが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. My heart knew.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "私、この歌声が出るようになったのは\n手術した後からだって言ったじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I gained the ability to sing like this\nafter my surgery. I told you that‚ remember?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 145.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "はい。それまでは、特に歌がうまいとか\n歌いたいって気持ちもあまりなかったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Until then‚ I wasn’t particularly good at singing‚\nand I didn’t really have a desire to sing either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "……だから、自分の声じゃないみたい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it doesn’t feel like your voice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 158.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "はい\nでも、それが当然なんだって思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nBut I came to think that was natural.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "本当は死ぬはずだったのが\n心臓をもらって生き延びたので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was supposed to be dead‚\nbut I extended my life by receiving a heart transplant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 167.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "それって、生まれ変わったってことじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t that basically the same as being reborn?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "俺は、そういう経験ないからよく分からないけど……\nそうかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not sure because I’ve never experienced anything like that.\nBut you might be right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 176.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
