      "text": "はい。だから今までとは違う自分になった気で\nこの胸が教えてくれる通りにやってみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. That’s why I work under the assumption that I’m a different person‚\nand I do exactly what my heart tells me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "いろんなことに挑戦したり\n今までの自分だったらやってないことをやってみたり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve taken on all sorts of challenges‚\ndone things I’ve never done before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "それで、アイドルまでやっちゃったんだもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that’s how you got all the way to being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 193.2
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 197.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "はい。でも……本当に大丈夫なのかなって……\nそれって本当の私なのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But… I wonder‚ is this really okay?\nIs this the real me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "急にこの声が出なくなったらどうしようって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if I suddenly can’t sing like this anymore?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 209.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "もしもグランプリの途中で\n急に前の私になっちゃったら、どうしようって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if‚ in the middle of the Grand Prix‚\nI suddenly turn back into my former self? What will I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 216.16666666666666
    },
    {
