      "text": "……それって……今ここにいるさくらは\n本当のさくらじゃないってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ are you saying that the Sakura standing here\nis not the real you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 222.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "…………分かりません\nでも、そうかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know.\nBut that may be so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "お医者さんにも言われたんです。移植して\nしばらくは、違和感を覚えることも多いって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The doctor told me as much. When people get transplants‚\nit’s common for them to feel disoriented for a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "だから私、あまり考えないようにって……\n前向きに全部受け入れようって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I decided not to really think about it.\nAnd to just stay positive and say yes to everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 241.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらが初めて事務所に来た時は）\n（そこまで考えているなんて少しも思わなかった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The first time Sakura came to the agency‚)\n(I never realized she’d put that much thought into it.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_03-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらの明るい振る舞いの裏を）\n（見抜けなかった……マネージャー失格だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I couldn’t see behind her bright‚ cheerful facade.)\n(I’m such a failure as her manager.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
